      <p class="hero-tagline">I edit, I lead, I build — usually all at once.</p>
      <span class="hero-scroll">Scroll ↓</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="s" id="about">
  <div class="s-label">About</div>
  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-photo">
      <img src="natalie-daher.png" alt="Natalie Daher">
    </div>
    <div class="about-body">
      <p>Hello! I'm an editorial leader based in Washington, DC, by way of New York. (🗣️ last name like Dare. It is 🇱🇧.)</p>

      <p>I currently serve as a director, planning &amp; special projects at Axios. I lead newsroom-wide strategy across web, newsletters, video and live events — shaping daily coverage while aligning long-term priorities across our National, Local and Pro divisions. In 2025, I was also selected for the <a href="https://www.journalists.org/womens-leadership-accelerator" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Online News Association's Women's Leadership Accelerator</a>, which has brought me valuable &amp; intensive leadership training and coaching in 2026.</p>

      <p>I've worked in newspapers, broadcast, startups and digital-native newsrooms — and across text, video and social formats — which has shaped my belief that great journalism requires both strong editorial judgment and strong systems. 😎</p>

      <div class="about-highlights-label">Wins from my time at Axios</div>
      <ul>
        <li>🗳️ <strong>Coordinating</strong> our newsroom-wide 2024 election coverage across our National, Local and Pro teams</li>
        <li>📺 <strong>Launching</strong> and executive producing "The Axios Show," an interview series with newsmakers across politics, business, tech and culture</li>
        <li>📧 <strong>Editing</strong> and writing for web and newsletters, including the flagship AM, PM &amp; Finish Line newsletters</li>
        <li>👩🏻‍💻 <strong>Contributing</strong> to strategy for producing, optimizing and delivering excellent journalism across Axios' platforms</li>
        <li>⚡ <strong>Designing</strong> and onboarding our newsroom-wide AirTable planning tool</li>
        <li>🗞️ <strong>Experimenting</strong> with new tools including live blogs</li>
        <li>👓 <strong>Managing</strong> and training editors and reporters on the breaking news team</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Before Axios,</strong> I worked as a digital editor at CNN Politics, leading digital coverage across assignment, breaking news and occasional features and analysis.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>At NowThis, I helped expand written products at the mobile-first newsroom known for reaching young audiences and learned how to video edit.</li>
        <li>I've also worked at CNBC and began my career as a reporter in the Midwest.</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>My essays and features</strong> have been published at publications including Lapham's Quarterly, Racked, HuffPost, CityLab, The Daily Beast and The Week.</p>

      <p><strong>I value mentorship</strong> inside and outside the newsroom and volunteered with the premiere writing organization for teenagers in New York City, <a href="https://girlswritenow.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Girls Write Now</a>, between 2018–2022. I am currently a co-lead of Axios' Women+ ERG.</p>

      <p>For opportunities or coffee dates, reach me at <a href="mailto:nataliedaher7@gmail.com">nataliedaher7@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-bottom">
    <div class="about-bottom-panel">
      <div class="about-bottom-head">Specialties &amp; skills 🗞️👩‍💻</div>
      <div class="tag-cloud">
        <span class="tag red">Managing teams &amp; strategy</span>
        <span class="tag red">Systems &amp; workflows</span>
        <span class="tag red">News coverage planning</span>
        <span class="tag">Editing breaking news</span>
        <span class="tag">Writing &amp; reporting</span>
        <span class="tag">Newsletters</span>
        <span class="tag">Video production &amp; editing</span>
        <span class="tag">Audience development</span>
        <span class="tag">Analytics &amp; insights</span>
        <span class="tag">Social media strategy</span>
        <span class="tag">Multi-platform strategy</span>
        <span class="tag">Branded/sponsored content</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-bottom-panel">
      <div class="about-bottom-head">My favorite things 🎶</div>
      <ul class="faves-grid">
        <li>Vinyl / live music</li>
